ze:11pt">about</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> not knowing what opportunities were available to them and how golf can better communicate and market the sport.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt 21.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">6.3</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The research highlights the importance that England Golf places on understanding the requirements of female segments and the ability to ac</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">t upon the findings.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">  In addition to implementing a specific women’s </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">marketing </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">campaign, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">County Golf Partnerships now focus on delivering </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">group taster and structured sessions for similar abilities</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> at</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">targeted facilities that are </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">friendly, accessible and af</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">fordable</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt 21.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt 21.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">6.4</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Many women and girls view golf as male dom</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">inated and feel self-conscious; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">women only groups are an ideal way to learn and support each other, it is also important that </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">participants experience playing the game from the earliest opportunity (</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">as opposed to just </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">receiving </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">coaching sessions).</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt 21.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">6.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">5</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Based on examples of best practice and in particular an extremely successful women’s programme called ‘Here come the girls’ run at Fynn Valley Golf Club in Suffolk, the following factors are vital:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">An </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">informal or flexible offer.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Delivered in groups, incorporating a social element.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Consistent lesson plans, delivered every two week</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> (less technical focus).</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">A stepping stone to club membership through follow on sessions.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Initially a free or low cos</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">t offer, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">leading to other cost</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> options.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">A requirement to track participation within a programme.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 1pt 31.36pt; padding-left:11.19pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Participants to share their experience through maintaining a journal.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 1pt 21.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">6.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">6</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">national </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">‘</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Get into golf</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">’ marketing campaign (</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ee </span><a href="http://www.getintogolf.org"><span style="color:#0563c1; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">www.getintogolf.org</span></a><span style="color:#0563c1; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; fo